Description :
        Read My Disciples Are All Big Villains Lu Zhou woke up and became the world's most powerful demonic patriarch, along with nine evil disciples who shocked the world. The first disciple has tens of thousands of demons under his command, and the second apprentice. Sword Demon will kill if he disagrees.. Without any cultivation, how to rescue these villains?
